    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduction to XML::Parser</title>

      <para>
        The XML::Parser module is a Perl interface to James Clark's XML parser.
        It is built on top of XML::Parser::Expat, which is a lower level interface to 
        the expat library. Each call to one of the parsing methods creates a new
        instance of XML::Parser::Expat which is then used to parse the document.
      </para>

      &lfs130_checked;

